race.comment: MAN OF THE TOWN (3) was a touch plain last time out but the three wins prior to start the campaign were full of merit. Is better than that run suggests and is capable of bouncing right back without surprising. ZOU BIG BOY (4) loves this course and distance with two wins and a second from just three attempts and will strip fitter second-up from the break. Rates highly on best figures and expected to go well. WIREWALKER (9) will be ready to peak now fourth run back and gets in well at the weights with the claim. Top-three conveyance. SMART AS SMART (6) rounds out the selections in a competitive contest.
